{"tid":364113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美少數黨領袖佩洛西：三子入獄「撼動世界的良心」　中國違兩制承諾","createTime":"2017-08-18T06:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T15:54:25.000Z","uid":23707,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ade83d2dbe792d600717e464c2c8c994d6c7c1cf","tid":364113,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:27:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E6%A1%88-%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B8%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96%E4%BD%A9%E6%B4%9B%E8%A5%BF-%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%90%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84-%E6%92%BC%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%89%AF%E5%BF%83-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%95%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25B0%2591%25E6%2595%25B8%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E9%25A0%2598%25E8%25A2%2596%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E6%25B4%259B%25E8%25A5%25BF-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%258D%2584-%25E6%2592%25BC%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%2589%25AF%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AB%25BE%2F&d=0Lgp8NwZPwstBGwhIg5L5p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=a35b66fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25B0%2591%25E6%2595%25B8%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E9%25A0%2598%25E8%25A2%2596%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E6%25B4%259B%25E8%25A5%25BF-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%258D%2584-%25E6%2592%25BC%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%2589%25AF%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AB%25BE%2F&h=1eb60ce9\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E6%A1%88-%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B8%E9%BB%A8%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96%E4%BD%A9%E6%B4%9B%E8%A5%BF-%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%90%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84-%E6%92%BC%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E7%9A%84%E8%89%AF%E5%BF%83-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%95%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6%E6%89%BF%E8%AB%BE/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國會眾議院少數黨領袖佩洛西（Nancy Pelosi）發表聲明回應「雙學三子」被改判入獄事件，指裁決是中國違背「一國兩制」承諾的最新證據，並形容昨日是「民主黑暗的一日」（dark day for democracy）。<br />\n<br />\n涉及三年前926公民廣場案的「雙學三子」，香港眾志主席羅冠聰、秘書長黃之鋒及學聯前秘書長周永康，昨日分別被判囚 6 至 8 個月，即時收監。<br />\n<br />\n繼美國眾議院議員Chris Smith及佛羅里達州聯邦參議員魯比奧（Marco Antonio Rubio），發表聯合聲明回應裁決之後，美國國會眾議院少數黨領袖、民主黨籍眾議員佩洛西（Nancy Pelosi）亦發表聲明跟進事件。<br />\n<br />\n法院的裁決使爭取普選的民主抗爭者未來五年無法參與競選，佩洛西批評是以「不公義和卑劣」的手段阻止香港人對民主的追求。她認為法院的決定「過份」（egregious），三子入獄「撼動世界的良心（shock the conscience of the world）」。裁決不但侵犯香港本有的自由和民主價值，更是中國違背「一國兩制」承諾的最新證據，應該受到國際社會的譴責。她重申美國道德上有責任就不公義事件發聲，即使與華有貿易來往，亦不應因此而噤若寒蟬。<br />\n<br />\n佩洛西又指，雨傘運動之後，中國加強鎮壓人權的力度，破壞港人自由，但民主運動將會繼續發展，而且會愈來愈壯大。在「民主黑暗的一日」（dark day for democracy），她向三子和支持自由的香港人送上支持，「任何壓迫和恐嚇都不會打擊人們追求普選、自由和公義的夢想」。"},{"pid":"206d443619bbef4eed5ea3f8de470f44386b5477","tid":364113,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:28:08.000Z","msg":"邊撚個❓"},{"pid":"0122ff9664bbb27cd5ad70864fd0d36db1a18a0c","tid":364113,"uid":99364,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:35:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f928a3fe7ae2e567ef4de114eb42556523c493c3","tid":364113,"uid":40628,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:38:41.000Z","msg":"五毛又想屌人齋講唔做，想散播灰心信訊<br />\n<br />\n人地講又屌唔講又屌<br />\n<br />\n唔好中計"},{"pid":"3b60d566e6eb36055b39145b63f9a4234b84559b","tid":364113,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:38:42.000Z","msg":"嚇兩嚇中國口交部又要出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33e43c1c29f5b1992017a55c912bc1fd1281c3e","tid":364113,"uid":2404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:39